Synchrony
The Synchrony Collection is inspired by the blending of artistic performance and fashion, silhouetted with the freedom to express. Synchrony is designed to be worn together and was created for ISOKO by creative director Oghalé Alex.

shop connection
Are you ready to connect?
As gratitude for allowing us to be part of your routine, we want to grant you exclusive early access to our collections. Members will receive two hours for SMS and one hour for email.
In your inbox you will also find our calming playlist waiting for you so that you can plug in and tune out as well as our weekly ISOKO editorials and wallpaper packs to bring you into our visual language and how we see the world.
